    <div class="content">
        <h2>Commitment to Accessibility</h2>
        <p>At Relsa Technologies, we are committed to ensuring that our website is accessible to everyone, including individuals with disabilities. We strive to adhere to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, which provide recommendations for making web content more accessible. We are constantly working to improve accessibility and to meet the needs of all visitors to our website.</p>

        <h2>Accessibility Features</h2>
        <p>Our website includes the following features to improve accessibility:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Text alternatives for non-text content, including images and videos.</li>
            <li>Keyboard navigation support for users who cannot use a mouse.</li>
            <li>Clear and consistent navigation that works with screen readers.</li>
            <li>Text resize options to make content easier to read for individuals with visual impairments.</li>
            <li>Simple and easy-to-read language to ensure that all users can understand our content.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Accessibility Improvements</h2>
        <p>We are always looking for ways to improve our website's accessibility. If you encounter any accessibility issues while browsing our site, please contact us so we can address them as quickly as possible. Your feedback is invaluable in helping us create a more accessible and inclusive website.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you need any assistance with accessing our website or have suggestions on how we can improve our accessibility, please get in touch with us:</p>
        <p>Email: accessibility@relsatechnologies.com</p>
        <p>Phone: 0800-123-4567</p>
